  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BaseConfigurationPanel
    Panel to visualize a base configuration summary and to let the user select parts of it.
    ComponentRightsPanel
    Panel to visualize sets of component (control interface or module) rights and to let the user alter them.
    ConfigPanel
    Container for a set of ConfigValuePanels.
    ConfigValuePanel
    Panel to visualize a ConfigValue.
    ConnectionGraphPanel
    Visualizes connections between modules/ports as an interactive graph.
    ConnectionGraphPanel.FindRelaxingSpotLayout

    ConnectionInfoPanel
    Provides context information on a selected connection in the advanced CI.
    ConnectionManagementPanel
    Visualizes (in)active connection and provides ways to manage them.
    ConnectionPrioritySelectionPanel
    Simple dialog to select priority of a new port connection.
    GeneralInfoPanel
    Provides general information when nothing is selected in the advanced CI.
    LogPanel
    Panel to visualize all of the system's events and to let the user filter them.
    MessagePanel
    Simple Panel to visualize a message, an optional icon/symbol and an optional checkbox.
    ModuleCISupportedCommandsPanel
    Panel to display supported commands of a module and to let the user access them.
    ModuleInfoPanel
    Provides context information on a selected module in the advanced CI.
    PortInfoPanel
    Provides context information on a selected port in the advanced CI.
    StringMapViewAndEditPanel
    Panel used to view and modify String maps.
    TableSelectionScrollPane
    Visualizes a sortable and modifiable table inside a dynamic JScrollPane.
    TextInputPanel
    A simple text input panel for dialogs.
